{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"alias":"sue-skimp-tear","description":"## Summary\nrebar's LLM runner inherits `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL` from the environment, so when a local\nClaude-Code payload-optimizing proxy (headroom, `http://127.0.0.1:8787`) is enabled, ALL\nof rebar's agentic LLM calls are routed through it. That proxy corrupts rebar's **agentic\ntool-loop** requests (Pass-2 plan-review verifier, completion-verifier), producing an empty\nprovider stream. The empty stream surfaces as `UnexpectedModelBehavior(\"Streamed response\nended without content or tool calls\")`, is caught at `runner.py:333` as a terminal\n`LLMUnavailableError` (no retry), and fail-closes the plan-review verdict to INDETERMINATE —\nwhich writes no attestation, so **every code-grounded ticket becomes un-claimable**.\n\n## Reproduction Steps\n1. Enable headroom (`ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8787`).\n2. `rebar review-plan <code-grounded-epic>` (e.g. ac1b-cef3-35c8-415f).\n3. Observe `coverage.verify_failed=True`, `coverage.metrics.verify_requests=0`,\n   `coverage.verify_error` = \"Streamed response ended without content or tool calls\",\n   verdict INDETERMINATE.\n\nExpected: verify completes; verdict PASS/BLOCK on the plan's merits.\nActual: verify makes 0 requests; verdict INDETERMINATE; claim refused (\"attestation stale\").\n\nDiscriminating proof: `env -u ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL rebar review-plan <same>` → verify_requests=20,\nverify_error=None, verdict PASS. Single-turn and simple/large tool-use streams pass through\nheadroom fine; only the multi-turn agentic tool-LOOP breaks. RTK (bash hook) is not involved.\n\n## Fix\nrebar's internal agent must not route through a local (loopback) Claude-Code payload optimizer.\nWhen the resolved model is Anthropic and `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL` points at a loopback host, build the\nAnthropic model with a provider pinned to the direct public API (bypassing the local proxy).\nRespect non-loopback gateways (untouched). Opt out with `REBAR_LLM_ALLOW_LOCAL_PROXY=1`.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] With `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL` set to a loopback host, rebar's runner builds an Anthropic model\n      whose provider base_url is the direct public API (`https://api.anthropic.com`), not the loopback.\n- [ ] A non-loopback `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL` (a real gateway) is respected (passed through unchanged).\n- [ ] `REBAR_LLM_ALLOW_LOCAL_PROXY=1` opts back in (no bypass) for users who intend the local proxy.\n- [ ] Non-Anthropic providers and the test model_override path are unaffected.\n- [ ] Unit test covers loopback-bypass / non-loopback-passthrough / opt-out; existing runner tests pass.\n- [ ] Replication: with headroom running, `rebar review-plan ac1b-cef3-35c8-415f` yields a determinate\n      verdict (verify_requests>0), not INDETERMINATE.","id":"454a-9266-ada6-43cc","parent_id":"","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"bug","title":"runner routes agentic LLM calls through local headroom proxy -> empty stream -> INDETERMINATE"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783351706337401001,"uuid":"317c000c-45be-4be4-abb6-45676d904cf0"}